  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c9c0bb15aa155f04c9e347da2bc948e0, type: 2}
    position: 1
    text: "\u0110\xE2y l\xE0 Richard, Nh\u1ECB Ho\xE0ng T\u1EED c\u1EE7a Ph\u01B0\u01A1ng
      B\u1EAFc."
    emotion: 1
    textSpeed: 0
    portraitEffect: 0
    effectDuration: 0
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 08bd7c046bacb1143878bcce1e8f3d20, type: 3}
    backgroundEffect: 0
    backgroundEffectDuration: 0
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    textSound: {fileID: 0}
    otherCharacters:
    - character: {fileID: 0}
      position: 2
      emotion: 3
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c9c0bb15aa155f04c9e347da2bc948e0, type: 2}
    position: 1
    text: "L\xE0 m\u1ED9t ng\u01B0\u1EDDi v\xF4 n\u0103ng trong th\u1EBF gi\u1EDBi
      t\u1ED3n t\u1EA1i ph\xE9p thu\u1EADt."
    emotion: 1
    textSpeed: 0
    portraitEffect: 0
    effectDuration: 0
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 08bd7c046bacb1143878bcce1e8f3d20, type: 3}
    backgroundEffect: 0
    backgroundEffectDuration: 0
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    textSound: {fileID: 0}
    otherCharacters:
    - character: {fileID: 0}
      position: 2
      emotion: 3
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c9c0bb15aa155f04c9e347da2bc948e0, type: 2}
    position: 1
    text: "Khi l\xEAn 13, c\u1EADu quy\u1EBFt \u0111\u1ECBnh \u0111i sang ph\u01B0\u01A1ng
      T\xE2y h\u1ECDc t\u1EADp. Nh\u1EB1m b\xF9 \u0111\u1EAFp khuy\u1EBFt \u0111i\u1EC3m
      v\xF4 n\u0103ng c\u1EE7a b\u1EA3n th\xE2n."
    emotion: 1
    textSpeed: 0
    portraitEffect: 0
    effectDuration: 0
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 08bd7c046bacb1143878bcce1e8f3d20, type: 3}
    backgroundEffect: 0
    backgroundEffectDuration: 0
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    textSound: {fileID: 0}
    otherCharacters:
    - character: {fileID: 0}
      position: 2
      emotion: 3
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c9c0bb15aa155f04c9e347da2bc948e0, type: 2}
    position: 1
    text: "C\u1EADu \u0111\xE3 n\u1ED7 l\u1EF1c h\u1ECDc t\u1EADp d\u01B0\u1EDBi
      s\u1EF1 ch\u1EC9 d\u1EA1y c\u1EE7a Cedric, kh\xF4ng ng\u1EEBng c\u1ED1 g\u1EAFng
      trong 5 n\u0103m. V\xE0 \u0111\xE3 t\u1ED1t nghi\u1EC7p. Sau \u0111\xF3 c\u1EADu
      quy\u1EBFt \u0111\u1ECBnh tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1 ph\u01B0\u01A1ng b\u1EAFc \u0111\u1EC3
      ra chi\u1EBFn tr\u01B0\u1EDDng. "
    emotion: 1
    textSpeed: 0
    portraitEffect: 0
    effectDuration: 0
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 08bd7c046bacb1143878bcce1e8f3d20, type: 3}
    backgroundEffect: 0
    backgroundEffectDuration: 0
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
